                               'Ixty' 1.0

                           by Charles-N. Jacob

  'Ixty' is a @{" Workbench game " link play} where you have to place various
shapes on a square 8 by 8 spaces game board. Each shape has
diagonal 'links' that prevents it to be next diagonally to another
shape of the same type... However, two or more shapes of the same
type can be next to each other either vertically or horizontally.

  Have fun!

