@node play "The game: Installation/Playing"

                             Installation

  The installation is very simple, just place "Ixty" where you
want on your hard drive, floppy disk, Ram Disk, etc. No other files
or Libraries are needed. However, the game requires a 68020(+)
Amiga with Workbench 2.0 or higher.

                             How to play?

  To play, just click on an empty space (where a small square is
located), and the shape that appears under 'Next' at the right of
the game board, will go to that position, if it is possible...

  You are allowed to place shapes of the same type next to each
other, either horizontally or vertically, but not diagonally...

  The game ends when it is no longer possible to place a shape...

  Have fun!

  You can quit the game by clicking on the game window's close
button or by pressing on the 'Esc' key.

@endnode

